title: Dakine Heli Pro 20L
description:
Check out 360° views of the 2015 Heli Pro 20L Pack.
Features: 
- Vertical snowboard carry
- Diagonal ski carry
- Fleece lined goggle pocket
- Hydration compatible
- Non-padded sleeve fits most 15" laptops
- Organizer pocket
- Padded waist belt
- Integrated rescue whistle / sternum strap
